### Auth Service - Development Environment
### Base URL: https://dev-api-id.execute-api.region.amazonaws.com/dev/auth

### Environment Variables
@baseUrl = https://dev-api-id.execute-api.region.amazonaws.com/dev/auth
@contentType = application/json

### Test Data for Development
@testEmail = dev-test@example.com
@testPassword = DevPassword123!
@testName = Dev Test User

### Development Environment Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Development User Registration
POST {{baseUrl}}/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{testEmail}}",
  "password": "{{testPassword}}",
  "name": "{{testName}}"
}

